時後，以<span style=\"color: red;\">3比2</span>裁定司機死於不合法被殺，即<span style=\"color: red;\">同意涉箍頸警員誤殺司機</span>。<br />\n<br />\n案發於2012年11月11日晚上，事主陳輝旺（終年65歲）在西隧收費亭附近，因車資問題與日籍乘客爭執動武。警察接報到場，調查後因事主打乘客，以普通襲擊拘捕他。事主由數名警員合力帶上警車，其間不斷掙扎，警員林偉榮疑箍到事主頸部，事主最終送院治理。兩日後，院方發現<span style=\"color: red;\">事主頸椎移位，引致全身癱瘓</span>，留院治療一個月後，於同年12月12日因支氣管肺炎死亡。"},{"pid":"616466a415ac62bd8c152fdf53b12207393188fe","tid":875446,"uid":136186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T02:07:48.000Z","msg":"肺炎死關事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> bio高手請指教"},{"pid":"216737209917ab934eb1ba30396d56414386a8cd","tid":875446,"uid":16061,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"616466a415ac62bd8c152fdf53b12207393188fe","tid":875446,"uid":136186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T02:07:48.000Z","msg":"肺炎死關事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> bio高手請指教"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T02:09:32.000Z","msg":"併發症"},{"pid":"d88e8977f069a352d0a6126a333528589786e918","tid":875446,"uid":153239,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"616466a415ac62bd8c152fdf53b12207393188fe","tid":875446,"uid":136186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T02:07:48.000Z","msg":"肺炎死關事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> bio高手請指教"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T02:10:04.000Z","msg":"比d邏輯諗下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢咁講 明顯係講出左事先會因肺炎而死"},{"pid":"815b8669d62c9d7c896e4f3ae1a647c7ca6c9959","tid":875446,"uid":107405,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"616466a415ac62bd8c152fdf53b12207393188fe","tid":875446,"uid":136186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T02:07:48.000Z","msg":"肺炎死關事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> bio高手請指教"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T02:17:17.000Z","msg":"一般而言，人體的組織只要能夠發揮50%的功能，便足以應付日常各種活動所需。<br />\n<br />\n　　所以，脊